PCI_FindByID  (&5038E)
#Parent PCI_
=>	R3 =	0 to start, or R3 last found
	R0 =	vendor ID (or -1 for wildcard)
	R1 =	device ID (or -1 for wildcard)
	R2 =	subsystem vendor ID (or -1 for wildcard)
	R4 =	subsystem ID (or -1 for wildcard)
<=	R3 =	<function handle=>PCI_fhand>

Finds the function handle based on the wildcarded information passed in.
